  <div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Let's Connect</h1>
    <p class="lead">Feel free to reach out for collaboration ideas! I'm always open to new projects and opportunities.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container my-5">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Contact Me</h1>
